public class Tabs extends BaseComponent<HTMLElement,Tabs> implements Attachable, org.patternfly.style.Modifiers.Box<HTMLElement,Tabs>, Expandable<HTMLElement,Tabs>, org.patternfly.style.Modifiers.Fill<HTMLElement,Tabs>, HasItems<HTMLElement,Tabs,Tab>, org.patternfly.style.Modifiers.PageInsets<HTMLElement,Tabs>, org.patternfly.style.Modifiers.Secondary<HTMLElement,Tabs>, org.patternfly.style.Modifiers.Vertical<HTMLElement,Tabs>
